# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AWS Deploy Kit - Build-Time Arguments
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to 'deploy-build-args' and fill in your values:
#   cp deploy-build-args.example deploy-build-args
#
# These NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are passed as --build-arg to `docker build`.
# Next.js inlines them into the client JS bundle at build time.
# They are NOT injected at runtime via SSM (see deploy-secrets for those).
#
# FORMAT: KEY=VALUE, one per line. Comments (#) and blank lines are ignored.
# NEVER commit deploy-build-args -- it may contain sensitive build config.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

NEXT_PUBLIC_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_recaptcha_site_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_ARCGIS_API_KEY=your_arcgis_api_key
